{"tid":2225363,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台灣藝人上CCTV講「在中國台灣等你」 小粉紅好High︰愛國好青年","createTime":"2020-10-01T09:09:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-01T11:37:18.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"0d37bca3bf928f1bd610340c36ad5c9ded2b53d2","tid":2225363,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T09:09:56.000Z","msg":"綜合媒體報導，現年19歲、以韓國選秀節目《Produce 101 S2》出道的前Wanna One成員賴冠霖，自團體解散後，就把演藝重心轉往中國，他今天將會出現在央視《江山如畫國慶音樂會》裡，並和其他中國藝人演唱《龍的傳人》。<br />\n<br />\n稍早央視在微博PO出賴冠霖的個人宣傳片段，影片中他開頭就表示「我是賴冠霖，我在中國台北等你」，接著又強調「台灣省台北市」，還說有不少美食，鹽酥雞、鳳梨酥等等。<br />\n<br />\n這其實已經不是賴冠霖第一次如此表態，他過去在選秀期間就已經自稱「來自中國台灣」，無論是在韓國或是中國皆是用「中國台灣」來自介，而這次明確的說法更是讓不少中國網友視他如瑰寶，留言大喊「政治立場一直很堅定三觀超正的小朋友」、「愛國好青年賴冠霖」、「根正苗紅賴冠霖」、「三觀正愛國的奶罐」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/10/01/phpKe4tYK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F10%2F01%2FphpKe4tYK.jpg&h=5cacbfd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3309136\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3309136&d=2MheXYw%2FBwPqfvV%2BE34w12INpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=7079c80d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3309136&h=47340904\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3309136</a>"},{"pid":"4f523dc9fe5de10504bae4adf32d57b5289f21be","tid":2225363,"uid":75337,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T09:12:21.000Z","msg":"聽都未聽過"},{"pid":"c345698475c8052b7b4192a3fa6d23bdbfd84132","tid":2225363,"uid":95138,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T09:13:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2838c26e8973cbc1d9d1eff4190eca5f019792bf","tid":2225363,"uid":353256,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T09:14:27.000Z","msg":"根據反滲透法係咪可以拉咗佢"},{"pid":"cf720887df452be362d9f4bc31b97bbb78b3ff1c","tid":2225363,"uid":219337,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T09:15:21.000Z","msg":"個樣柒撚到唔怪得知要解散<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb7bdfad8837dca6cd8fbb9647c2664b12fb7ce5","tid":2225363,"uid":275370,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T09:15:27.000Z","msg":"奶支狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"961cae8e41ebcca645a7a80db0d57db51e79162c","tid":2225363,"uid":119223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T09:16:09.000Z","msg":"新型冠狀武漢"},{"pid":"fba85ed2c269783115ea5d7143e00b27e4e48ed9","tid":2225363,"uid":189046,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T09:17:31.000Z","msg":"言論及爭議事件<br />\n來自「中國臺灣」<br />\n<br />\n賴冠霖第一次參加《Produce 101 S2》錄影時（2017年2月26日錄影，4月7日播出）自我介紹來自臺灣，其後節目官方於網路釋出的自我介紹影片裡表示自己來自臺北[10]。2017年3月9日，《Produce 101 S2》練習生全員出演Mnet《M COUNTDOWN》，結束後在上岩洞CJ E&amp;M 中心廣場與粉絲見面並分送事先準備好之小禮物及自介紙卡，賴冠霖的自介紙卡後經公開於微博，屬名中國臺灣賴冠霖，此舉動引起部分臺灣網友的批判[11]，不過介紹文為他親筆手寫之事真實性有待商榷。[12][13]<br />\n<br />\n2017年8月，賴冠霖於韓國廣播節目《Kiss The Radio》裡說出中國臺灣四個字，此舉動再次造成部分臺灣網友的批評。[14]<br />\n<br />\n2018年2月14日，賴冠霖於第七屆Gaon榜音樂頒獎典禮，代表團體用中文發表得獎感言。他首先表示：「謝謝主辦方給我們這個獎，以這個獎為動力，2018也會展現更好的Wanna One給你們！」，但在之後說道「也謝謝網易雲音樂！大家請多多用網易雲音樂」，得獎感言突如其來的業配贊助廠商而引發了爭議。[15]<br />\n微博轉發護旗手<br />\n<br />\n2019年8月4日，在個人微博轉發中華人民共和國國旗，並宣布「我是護旗手」。[16][17][18]<br />\n微博轉發支持香港警察<br />\n<br />\n2019年8月14日，在個人微博轉發人民日報官微貼文，並發表「#我也支持香港警察# 🇨🇳 🇨🇳 🇨🇳」。[19][20]"},{"pid":"0512a93e0345efc013b913122d20d54ef6e05aac","tid":2225363,"uid":200877,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T09:19:38.000Z","msg":"佢落足力奶共都紅唔起 微博得600萬followers<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4662ea84c3e8c49e190337209feb37c96f27a367","tid":2225363,"uid":186997,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T09:21:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media0.giphy.com/media/DTbnzI5Ve1lfi/source.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia0.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FDTbnzI5Ve1lfi%2Fsource.gif&h=ddfb7da2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cd8ac42a55f4cd23de7695d75e9cd6ae48c9a08e","tid":2225363,"uid":378793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T09:25:57.000Z","msg":"奶共霖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81c495629fac364babbee89b5b5ecfa1cb55202d","tid":2225363,"uid":28181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T10:20:02.000Z","msg":"佢確定佢仲番到台灣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8a6451093fae552f8a7c157465823ab15f8b806","tid":2225363,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T11:08:04.000Z","msg":"台灣唔敢拉佢,言論自由就包有人做共匪,不過開戰就唔同講法"},{"pid":"6b666f03ce957d8c60d5f57d8c2b1264b7b8d35b","tid":2225363,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f8a6451093fae552f8a7c157465823ab15f8b806","tid":2225363,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T11:08:04.000Z","msg":"台灣唔敢拉佢,言論自由就包有人做共匪,不過開戰就唔同講法"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T11:37:18.000Z","msg":"言論自由唔係大晒喎<br />\n你試下係德國講納粹黨<br />\n係美國認係KKK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}